-- Tesco to Use Consumer Data to Judge Home Loans: Sunday Times
-- B y   E m m a   C h a r l t o n
-- 2012-08-05T07:41:41Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-05/tesco-to-use-consumer-data-to-judge-home-loans-sunday-times.html
Tesco Plc (TSCO) , the U.K.’s largest
retailer, plans to use shopping data to assess customers’
suitability for home loans, the Sunday Times  reported , citing
comments from a company executive.  Using the data “we can make a better assessment of risk,”
Benny Higgins, the chief executive officer of Tesco Bank, said,
according to the newspaper. “It’s about simplicity, about
transparency, about rewarding loyalty,” the report said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Emma Charlton in London at 
